headline: McKesson’s Practice Insights Designated as a 2026 Qualified Clinical Data Registry by Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services
summary: IRVING, Texas, January 20, 2026--For the tenth year, CMS named McKesson a Qualified Clinical Data Registry approved to participate in the Merit-based Incentive Payment System.
